# Exercise 1. Charactor Input.

#base question. Ask a user for name and age, then print a message with that info.
#      Also print a message with the year they will turn 100.


name = input("Enter your name: ")
age = input("Enter your age: ")

current_year = 2022
year_onehundred = current_year - int(age) + 100

print(f"Hello {name}! You are {age} years old.")
print(f"You will turn 100 in the year {year_onehundred}.")


